Shut up.

01:19.813 --> 01:21.582
He could be right, Miller.

01:21.615 --> 01:23.451
Ray is overreacting,
Booms, okay?

01:23.484 --> 01:25.586
Trust me, Janice does not want
to get back together.

01:25.619 --> 01:27.721
Oh, I didn't say she wanted
to get back together.

01:27.755 --> 01:29.323
