Christmas horny.

01:29.357 --> 01:30.391
(mouthing)

01:30.424 --> 01:31.759
And if you two guys have sex,

01:31.792 --> 01:33.661
it's gonna be drama
all over again around here.

01:33.694 --> 01:36.164
No, don't let that happen,
Miller.

01:36.197 --> 01:38.566
This was not a very pleasant
work environment

01:38.599 --> 01:39.900
after that divorce.

01:39.933 --> 01:42.170
Oh, come on. We always kept it
very professional.

01:42.203 --> 01:43.471
Really?

01:43.504 --> 01:46.340
Because I seem to remember
breaking up a spit fight

01:46.374 --> 01:47.441
in the parking lot.

01:47.475 --> 01:49.543
You both lost
your dignity.

01:49.577 --> 01:51.912
