to clown school for three weeks

07:17.571 --> 07:19.106
until it settled into a wave?

07:20.641 --> 07:22.676
And, Debbie,
when you wet your pants

07:22.710 --> 07:25.212
at your school talent show,
who pulled the fire alarm

07:25.245 --> 07:27.114
so your sorority sisters
wouldn't find out?

07:28.716 --> 07:30.618
Year after year, I've cleaned up
after your messes.

07:30.651 --> 07:31.752
And when Christmas rolls around,

07:31.785 --> 07:33.253
do I put you
on the naughty list?

07:33.286 --> 07:35.989
No, I make sure that
your Christmases are magical.

07:36.023 --> 07:39.560
And now, this one year,
when Mom's in a jam

07:39.593 --> 07:42.630
and needs your help,
you have the nerve to tell her

07:42.663 --> 07:45.966
she's made her bed
and there'll be no Christmas?!

07:47.668 --> 07:49.637
Merry Christmas!

07:49.670 --> 07:52.573
ALL:
Merry Christmas!

07:58.145 --> 08:01.048
And so that son of a gun
had the nerve

08:01.081 --> 08:03.917
to ride our tail for 15 miles.

08:03.951 --> 08:05.686
So, finally, at a red light,

08:05.719 --> 08:09.657
