damn flashing lights."

08:13.694 --> 08:15.729
And I bet Dad
wasn't even speeding.

08:15.763 --> 08:17.164
No.

08:17.197 --> 08:20.568
But it seems that we were
dragging a bicycle

08:20.601 --> 08:22.035
for a few miles.

08:22.069 --> 08:24.672
Watch this.

08:24.705 --> 08:27.575
See that puddle?
Yeah.

08:27.608 --> 08:29.242
Presto, right over it.
(chuckles)

08:31.645 --> 08:32.646
Look at you, Grandpa,

08:32.680 --> 08:36.149
