of kitchen spills.

08:36.183 --> 08:38.251
So, Nathan,
you and Janice

08:38.285 --> 08:40.053
are coming up
on an anniversary.

08:40.087 --> 08:42.656
Yeah, yeah,
four, uh, four years.

08:42.690 --> 08:44.625
What are you supposed
to get at four?

08:44.658 --> 08:46.927
Is it, uh, chairs
or personal space or...

08:46.960 --> 08:48.662
Oh, no, four is...
four is linen.

08:48.696 --> 08:49.797
And we're gonna
have to get

08:49.830 --> 08:52.733
new sheets for our bed
'cause the ones we have are all

08:52.766 --> 08:54.334
worn out, huh?
(laughs):
Oh!

08:54.367 --> 08:56.236
I wish your diaphragm
would wear out.

08:58.639 --> 09:01.775
