that they'll be cross-eyed

09:04.745 --> 09:06.246
or foggy-headed.

09:06.279 --> 09:08.916
So, Adam,
how's rehab?

09:10.283 --> 09:12.285
Did you see Lindsay Lohan
in there?

09:12.319 --> 09:15.155
I like her. She's got spunk.

09:15.188 --> 09:16.690
No, no celebrities.

09:16.724 --> 09:19.359
It's just me and my other
heroin addict friends.

09:19.392 --> 09:22.996
Mm. I know what it's like
to be addicted.

09:23.030 --> 09:28.235
My friend Alice got me hooked
on her grandson's ADD meds.

09:28.268 --> 09:32.239
I made a quilt
as long as my driveway.

09:34.107 --> 09:35.776
Uh, tell me something.

09:35.809 --> 09:37.277
Why'd I come in here again?

09:37.310 --> 09:38.912
Yeah, you smelled muffins,
Grandpa.

09:38.946 --> 09:40.147
Do you know what?

09:40.180 --> 09:41.782
