11:02.963 --> 11:04.197
How did this happen?

11:04.231 --> 11:08.068
Look, long insane story short,
my mom is making Janice and me

11:08.101 --> 11:10.904
pretend that we're still married
in front of my grandparents.

11:10.938 --> 11:12.205
And she looks good, man.

11:12.239 --> 11:14.274
The only way to stop myself
from getting aroused

11:14.307 --> 11:17.778
is to look at my grandma,
and that's weird.

11:17.811 --> 11:19.479
I'm scared, Ray.

11:19.512 --> 11:21.849
(whispers): I'm scared
that I'm Christmas horny.

11:21.882 --> 11:23.917
Damn it, Nate!

11:23.951 --> 11:25.953
