11:35.829 --> 11:37.230
I know, I know,
I know.

11:37.264 --> 11:38.799
Look,
I need help, man.

11:38.832 --> 11:39.800
I am losing control!

11:39.833 --> 11:41.268
I mean, my mind
is going places.

11:41.301 --> 11:43.070
I mean, maybe I'm more
than Christmas horny.

11:43.103 --> 11:44.337
Maybe this is a sign

11:44.371 --> 11:46.339
that Janice and I
need to get back together.

11:46.373 --> 11:48.876
So? There's a sign
right in front of me

11:48.909 --> 11:50.811
that says, "No talking
on cell phones."

11:50.844 --> 11:53.080
