a damn thing, Nate!

11:53.113 --> 11:55.883
JANICE: Nate, honey, you
need help down there?

11:55.916 --> 11:56.917
Is that Janice?

11:56.950 --> 11:58.418
Did she just call you "honey"?

11:58.451 --> 12:02.155
Well, you have definitely
got my vote, Congressman.

12:02.189 --> 12:03.924
(laughs)

12:03.957 --> 12:05.092
Stay strong, Nate!

12:06.426 --> 12:08.796
Oh, my God, don't leave me alone
up there like that.

12:08.829 --> 12:10.530
Your grandfather keeps
asking me to lay down

12:10.563 --> 12:12.132
so he can step over me.

12:13.834 --> 12:15.969
Listen, uh, thanks
again for doing this.

12:16.003 --> 12:18.271
Yeah, truth is, I didn't
really have much else going on.

12:18.305 --> 12:20.908
I was probably just gonna
drink a pint of vodka,

12:20.941 --> 12:22.976
then unwrap the gift
I wrapped for myself,

12:23.010 --> 12:25.012
which was just
more vodka.

12:27.014 --> 12:27.815
So...

12:27.848 --> 12:29.983
Not a great time of year
to be single.

12:30.017 --> 12:32.385
No, no, it's not.
It's not.

12:32.419 --> 12:33.987
Oh, by the way,
while we're on that subject,

12:34.021 --> 12:35.956
I just want to be clear
that I'm not sending you

12:35.989 --> 12:37.958
