why I asked you to do this.

12:37.991 --> 12:38.892
What do you mean?

12:38.926 --> 12:39.827
Well, I just think

12:39.860 --> 12:43.030
it would be dangerous
for us to, you know...

12:43.063 --> 12:44.397
deck each other's halls.

12:47.167 --> 12:48.936
Jingle each other's
bells, you know?

12:50.403 --> 12:52.239
